	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It's likely that the game uses "fixed point", where each speed is a fraction with a constant denominator. Can speeds in Game Maker be floating-point, or fraction, or decimal?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


