	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />yeah fraction and decimal.
<br />as in .2 or 1/5
<br />what would a float point be?
<br />
<br />It would be easier if FCEU XD had a frame-by-frame option.
<br />
<br />
<br />
<br />After examination it seems like speed 0f = 15 pixel movements out of 16 frames.
<br />
<br />so the speed would be 15/16.
<br />
<br />It does used fix points.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


